  <div class="_content u-dark-region">
      
  <div class="highlight-image">
    <h2 class="_title visible">Disability Cultural Center Library Guide</h2>
    <div class="_text"><p>The Disability Cultural Center collaborates with the UIC Libraries to provide resources related to disability culture, history, and identity to the UIC community.  The library guide linked here is intended to connect DCC visitors to resources available at the UIC Libraries.</p>
</div>
        <a href="https://researchguides.uic.edu/DCCLibraryGuide" class="_button button" target="_blank">
      DCC Library Guide
    </a>
      </div>

  </div>

</div>

      </div>
  
